1. There  is  no  Bank  into  the  world  that  would  give  money  to  somebody  that  is  NOT  their  client  and  have  NO  
Guarantee. 
2. There is no Bank into the world that would give money or take any risk for UNKNOWN customers that are also 
based outside of the country where this bank is based. 
3. There  is  no  Insurance  that  would  give  any  PPI  to  someone  that  is  NOT  their  customer,  that  has  NOT  guarantee 
and is not based into the same country of the bank 
